translation[7]{c,v,t}:
  2,106,Jiss aayat ko hum mansookh ker den ya bhula den iss say behtar ya iss jaisi aur latay hain kiya tu nahi janta kay Allah Taalaa her cheez per qadir hai
  2,107,Kiya tujhay nahi maloom kay zamin-o-aasman ka mulk Allah hi kay liye hai aur Allah kay siwa tumhara koi wali aur madadgar nahi
  2,108,Kiya tum apney rasool say yehi poochna chahatay ho jo iss say pehlay musa (alh-e-salam) poocha gaya tha? (suno) eman ko kufur say badalney wala seedhi raah say bhatak jata hai
  2,109,Inn ehal-e-kitab kay aksay log ba wajood haq wazeh ho janey kay mehaz hasad-o-bughz ki bina per tumhen bhi eman say hata dena chahatay hain tum bhi moad kero aur choro yahan tak kay Allah Taalaa apna hukum laye. Yaqeenan Allah Taalaa her cheez per qudrat rakhta hai
  2,110,Tum namazen qaeem rakho aur zakat detay raha kero aur jo kuch bhalaee tum apney liye aagay bhejo gay sab kuch Allah kay pass paa lo gay be-shak Allah Taalaa tumharay aemaalon ko khoob dekh raha hai
  2,111,Yeh kehtay hain kay jannat mein yahud-o-nasaaraa kay siwa aur koi na jayega yeh sirf inn ki aarzooyen hain inn say kaho agar tum sachay ho to koi daleel to paish kero
  2,112,Suno! Jo bhi apney aap ko khuloos kay sath Allah kay samney jhuka dey. Be-shak ussay uss ka rab poora badla dey ga iss per na to koi khof hoga na ghum aur udasi